   "cmc_fetchxml":"<fetch version=\"1.0\" output-format=\"xml-platform\" mapping=\"logical\" distinct=\"false\"><entity name=\"contact\"><attribute name=\"fullname\"/><attribute name=\"telephone1\"/><attribute name=\"contactid\"/><order attribute=\"fullname\" descending=\"false\"/><filter type=\"and\"><condition attribute=\"firstname\" operator=\"like\" value=\"%WeightedRoundRobin%\"/><condition attribute=\"createdon\" operator=\"today\"/></filter></entity></fetch>",

}
